{"tid":2027024,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"陳偉霆事隔一年用普通話再拍Chanel廣告：因為我太貪心了","createTime":"2020-05-21T09:34:28.000Z","updateTime":"2020-05-21T11:31:33.000Z","uid":130626,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"d53df160c404283814ae861936d1bd9a30d22b77","tid":2027024,"uid":130626,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-21T09:34:28.000Z","msg":"陳偉霆自從在內地走紅後，成為無數品搶手的對象。大家還記得上年他為Chanel拍攝的廣告呢？當時片中廣告約有45秒，他全程以英語說對白。事後香港網民反應兩極，其中他被網民狠批英文發音不正確，更笑他為何會說：「I really want to try」之後網上亦有很藝人及網紅惡搞這段影片，成為當時熱話。<br />\n<br />\n事隔一年他再度為Chanel拍攝同類型廣告，但可能吸取上一次被取笑的教訓，這次陳偉霆近乎以全普通話來說，這段影片可以在他的IG可以見。可是這次廣告影片只有幾句對白，並沒有太多特別的說話令大家印象深刻令網民記住，應該不大機會再度成為網上熱話確實有點可惜。<br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn.hk01.com/di/media/images/dw/20200521/340138120932626432.jpeg/_ixFvqAbzseQrNMZcFnt7kmTlluYENgakMFJuZDBSbk\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.hk01.com%2Fdi%2Fmedia%2Fimages%2Fdw%2F20200521%2F340138120932626432.jpeg%2F_ixFvqAbzseQrNMZcFnt7kmTlluYENgakMFJuZDBSbk&h=2560b25b&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn.hk01.com/di/media/images/dw/20200521/340138450542006272.png/-mQFDRLX7gaeDAWdYXTxEbWi8ffERplcGkUC1hpFAtY\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.hk01.com%2Fdi%2Fmedia%2Fimages%2Fdw%2F20200521%2F340138450542006272.png%2F-mQFDRLX7gaeDAWdYXTxEbWi8ffERplcGkUC1hpFAtY&h=b838defe&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"bac13d36d36e33074f4fdbd8a0f3bcc1b0bcb68f","tid":2027024,"uid":12628,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-05-21T09:40:28.000Z","msg":"Dont make 岸鳩famous"},{"pid":"32cbc643c37957127680a678e9bd75d964ef4efc","tid":2027024,"uid":98386,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"bac13d36d36e33074f4fdbd8a0f3bcc1b0bcb68f","tid":2027024,"uid":12628,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-05-21T09:40:28.000Z","msg":"Dont make 岸鳩famous"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-05-21T11:29:32.000Z","msg":"唔洗你make 佢已經好famous <br />\n身家億億聲住豪宅 反而你地兒登仔吹奏嗰個垃圾關屎斌真係連屎都不如<img src=\"/assets/face